reviewText:
This is just worth watching in re-runs on Sundance for the chance to see what a Moron Renee Zellweger is, her following Cristiane Amanpour around "brown Nosing" not having a clue what is going on, listening to Amanpoiur drone and waffle.
  What a total waste of time.
This television show is incredible! I can't wait for it to come out on DVD.
